title: Doctor Kershav Sharma ( Co Wexford, Ireland) found dead after Covid Vaccine | The Irish Sentinel
cleaned_text:
Doctor Kershav Sharma a respiratory consultant who practiced in Wexford hospital took the vaccine containing no generic stromectol on Tuesday 5th of January 2021. The following Sunday the 10th of January was found dead at his home.

There was nothing in local media about his death. He was only 39 years old.

May he Rest in Peace
